===Standard Redeem Script Patterns===

====P2SH-P2PK====
<pre>
Redeem: <pubkey> OP_CHECKSIG_DILITHIUM
ScriptSig: <signature> <redeem-script>
</pre>

====P2SH Time-Locked====
<pre>
Redeem: <locktime> OP_CHECKLOCKTIMEVERIFY OP_DROP <pubkey> OP_CHECKSIG_DILITHIUM
ScriptSig: <signature> <redeem-script>
</pre>

===INTcoin Adaptations===

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Component !! BIP 16 !! IIP-38
|-
| Hash function || RIPEMD160(SHA256) || SHA3-256[0:20]
|-
| Signature algorithm || ECDSA || ML-DSA-87
|-
| Signature opcode || OP_CHECKSIG || OP_CHECKSIG_DILITHIUM
|-
| Signature size || ~72 bytes || 4,627 bytes
|-
| Public key size || 33 bytes || 2,592 bytes
|-
| Address encoding || Base58Check || Bech32
|}

